snippet.title: Freddy & Friends: On Tour Episode 3
snippet.description:
Fazbear Entertainment has definitely hidden these episodes quite well, but our archival team managed to dig this up! Looks like Freddy and the gang are still touring, with Foxy on their tails - but why is everything shaking?
